#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.broadcast_to"
msgstr "# triton.language.broadcast_to"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:2
msgid "## 1 功能作用说明"
msgstr "## 1 Function Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:4
msgid "将张量广播到目标形状，自动处理维度对齐。广播操作不会复制数据，而是通过改变张量的形状和步长来实现。"
msgstr "Broadcasts a tensor to the target shape, automatically handling dimension alignment. The broadcast operation does not copy data but instead achieves it by changing the tensor's shape and stride."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:6
msgid "**语法：**"
msgstr "**Syntax:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:8
msgid ""
"- `triton.language.broadcast_to(input, shape)` - 函数调用形式\n"
"- `input.broadcast_to(shape)` - 成员函数形式\n"
msgstr ""
"- `triton.language.broadcast_to(input, shape)` - function call form\n"
"- `input.broadcast_to(shape)` - member function form\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:10
msgid "**功能：**"
msgstr "**Function:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:12
msgid ""
"- 自动处理维度对齐，将大小为1的维度扩展到目标形状中对应维度的大小\n"
"- 保持数据不变，仅改变张量的形状信息\n"
msgstr ""
"- Automatically handle dimension alignment by expanding dimensions of size 1 to match the corresponding dimension size in the target shape  \n"
"- Keep the data unchanged, only modify the shape information of the tensor\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:14
msgid "## 2 参数规格"
msgstr "## 2 Parameter Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:16
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:18
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 必需 | 说明 |\n"
"|--------|------|------|------|\n"
"| input | tensor | 是 | 输入张量 |\n"
"| shape | List[int] | 是 | 目标形状 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Required | Description |\n"
"|----------------|------|----------|-------------|\n"
"| input | tensor | Yes | Input tensor |\n"
"| shape | List[int] | Yes | Target shape |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:20
msgid "**返回值：**"
msgstr "**Return value:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:22
msgid ""
"- **类型：** tensor\n"
"- **形状：** 与shape参数指定的目标形状相同\n"
"- **数据类型：** 与输入张量相同\n"
"- **内存布局：** 通过改变步长信息实现广播，无数据拷贝\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Type:** tensor\n"
"- **Shape:** Same as the target shape specified by the `shape` parameter\n"
"- **Data type:** Same as the input tensor\n"
"- **Memory layout:** Broadcasting is achieved by modifying stride information, with no data copy\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:24
msgid "**约束条件：**"
msgstr "**Constraints:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:26
msgid ""
"- 输入张量的维度数必须等于目标形状的维度数\n"
"- 所有维度必须满足广播规则\n"
msgstr ""
"- The number of dimensions of the input tensor must equal the number of dimensions of the target shape.\n"
"- All dimensions must satisfy the broadcasting rules.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:28
msgid "### 2.2 DataType支持表"
msgstr "### 2.2 DataType Support Table"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:30
msgid ""
"| 支持情况 | int8 | int16 | int32 | int64 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | float16 | float32 | bfloat16 | float8e4 | float8e5 | float64 | bool |\n"
"|----------|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:------:|:------:|:-------:|:----:|:----:|:------:|:---:|\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | ✓ |\n"
"| GPU支持 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Support Status | int8 | int16 | int32 | int64 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | float16 | float32 | bfloat16 | float8e4 | float8e5 | float64 | bool |\n"
"|----------|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:------:|:------:|:-------:|:----:|:----:|:------:|:---:|\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | ✓ |\n"
"| GPU Support | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:32
msgid "### 2.3 Shape支持表"
msgstr "### 2.3 Shape Support Table"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:34
msgid "支持任意维度数、任意形状大小。"
msgstr "Supports any number of dimensions and any shape size."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:36
msgid "### 2.4 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.4 Special Limitations"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:38
msgid "与broadcast不同，Triton社区实现的broadcast_to必须保证tensor的shape和目标shape的rank一致"
msgstr "Unlike broadcast, the broadcast_to implemented by the Triton community must ensure that the rank of the tensor's shape matches the rank of the target shape."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:40
msgid "### 2.5 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.5 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:42
msgid "**基本用法：**"
msgstr "**Basic Usage:**"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast_to.md:44
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def matrix_add_bias_kernel(x_ptr, bias_ptr, output_ptr, M, N, BLOCK_M: tl.constexpr, BLOCK_N: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    # 加载数据块\n"
"    x = tl.load(x_ptr + offsets, mask=mask)\n"
"\n"
"    # 广播bias到匹配的形状\n"
"    bias = tl.load(bias_ptr)\n"
"    bias_broadcast = bias.broadcast_to([BLOCK_M, BLOCK_N])\n"
"\n"
"    # 执行加法\n"
"    output = x + bias_broadcast\n"
"    tl.store(output_ptr + offsets, output, mask=mask)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

